## Early game

**Io** on Jupiter (Defense) is the classic Oxium farm: the wiki cites roughly
80 Oxium over 10 waves here, all from Oxium Ospreys that must be shot down by
a player (they don't drop anything if they self-destruct first). It's low
enough level for a new account to run comfortably, and every Osprey kill is an
enemy drop, so Resource Drop Boosters and Resourceful Retriever both help.

## Mid & late game

**Tycho** on Lua (Survival, Steel Path) scales the same idea up: higher enemy
levels mean more Oxium Ospreys spawn per minute, so a long Survival rotation
here comfortably outpaces resetting Io over and over. Europa's **Paimon** and
Pluto's **Outer Terminus** (both Defense) are solid alternatives if Tycho's
squad isn't available.

